"Pointer trail"/en
===
¶Move your pointer to draw a fading rainbow trail. @Previous (←←) remembers the last five @Pointer places, and @List.translate draws a dot for each, fading and shifting color from oldest to newest.¶
history•[Place]: ←← 5 Pointer()
Stage(history.translate(
		ƒ(spot•Place index•#)
			Phrase('●'
				color: Color(75% 100 index × 40°)
				opacity: index ÷ history.length()
				place: Place(spot.x spot.y))))
